gomodel:SYNGO_2192  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: BCR was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\nBCR was localized in spines and dendrites.. Experimental description: Materials and Methods\nAnimals.\nMale Sprague Dawley rats were used for experiments including dissociated hippocampal culture, immunoblot analysis, in vivo coimmunoprecipitation, and electron microscopy." ;
